WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:05.000
♪♪

00:09.000 --> 00:19.000
♪♪

00:19.000 --> 00:23.000
♪♪

00:23.000 --> 00:24.000
Mother! Mother!

00:25.000 --> 00:26.000
Mother.

00:26.000 --> 00:29.000
What did they do to you?

00:29.000 --> 00:36.000
♪♪

00:36.000 --> 00:37.000
How could you do this?!

00:37.000 --> 00:39.000
She saved your life!

00:39.000 --> 00:42.000
♪♪

00:42.000 --> 00:44.000
Relax.

00:44.000 --> 00:45.000
I have her eyes.

00:45.000 --> 00:47.000
The witch is dead.

00:47.000 --> 00:49.000
Praise Sol.

00:47.000 --> 00:49.000
Marcus: Praise Sol.

00:49.000 --> 00:51.000
Campion: Mother.

00:51.000 --> 00:55.000
♪♪

00:55.000 --> 00:56.000
It's going to be okay.

00:56.000 --> 00:58.000
It'll be okay,

00:56.000 --> 00:58.000
Mother.

00:58.000 --> 00:59.000
Put her in the silo.

00:58.000 --> 00:59.000
No.

00:59.000 --> 01:01.000
Go away!

00:59.000 --> 01:01.000
Don't come near me!

01:01.000 --> 01:02.000
No! [ Grunts ]

01:03.000 --> 01:04.000
Aah!

01:03.000 --> 01:04.000
Leave her alone!

01:04.000 --> 01:06.000
She can't do anything

01:04.000 --> 01:06.000
without her eyes!

01:06.000 --> 01:09.000
♪♪

01:09.000 --> 01:11.000
Stop!

01:09.000 --> 01:11.000
You're hurting her!

01:11.000 --> 01:15.000
Aah!

01:11.000 --> 01:15.000
Let her go!

01:15.000 --> 01:17.000
Back away.

01:17.000 --> 01:20.000
Leave her alone

01:17.000 --> 01:20.000
or I'll kill you all!

01:20.000 --> 01:21.000
It's okay.

01:21.000 --> 01:23.000
It's okay.

01:21.000 --> 01:23.000
I'll kill you!

01:23.000 --> 01:25.000
Stand down.

01:23.000 --> 01:25.000
Listen to me.

01:25.000 --> 01:27.000
We're not here

01:25.000 --> 01:27.000
to hurt you,

01:27.000 --> 01:29.000
and I know you don't want

01:27.000 --> 01:29.000
to hurt anyone,

01:29.000 --> 01:32.000
so just

01:29.000 --> 01:32.000
hand over the gun.

01:32.000 --> 01:36.000
Campion, remember...

01:36.000 --> 01:39.000
violence won't help.

01:39.000 --> 01:40.000
Put it down.

01:40.000 --> 01:41.000
[ Groans ]

01:42.000 --> 01:43.000
Give him the gun.

01:44.000 --> 01:53.000
♪♪

01:54.000 --> 02:03.000
♪♪

02:03.000 --> 02:06.000
Don't want

02:03.000 --> 02:06.000
to leave you, Mother.

02:06.000 --> 02:07.000
You'll be fine.

02:07.000 --> 02:16.000
♪♪

02:16.000 --> 02:17.000
No!

02:17.000 --> 02:21.000
Don't put me in here!

02:17.000 --> 02:21.000
I want to be with Mother!

02:21.000 --> 02:22.000
Can't do that.

02:22.000 --> 02:24.000
Not after that little stunt

02:22.000 --> 02:24.000
you just pulled.

02:24.000 --> 02:27.000
It's just for a little while,

02:24.000 --> 02:27.000
until I can figure it out,

02:27.000 --> 02:28.000
how I can help you.

02:28.000 --> 02:30.000
You're a liar.

02:28.000 --> 02:30.000
You don't want to help me.

02:30.000 --> 02:31.000
Is that

02:30.000 --> 02:31.000
what Earth was?

02:31.000 --> 02:33.000
Just a bunch

02:31.000 --> 02:33.000
of lies?

02:33.000 --> 02:36.000
Do any of you tell the truth

02:33.000 --> 02:36.000
about anything?

02:36.000 --> 02:38.000
Not really,

02:36.000 --> 02:38.000
kid.

02:38.000 --> 02:39.000
Let me out.

02:39.000 --> 02:41.000
I want

02:39.000 --> 02:41.000
to be with Mother!

02:41.000 --> 02:44.000
Let me out!

02:44.000 --> 02:46.000
Reinforce this door.

02:46.000 --> 02:56.000
♪♪

02:56.000 --> 03:06.000
♪♪

03:06.000 --> 03:15.000
♪♪

03:15.000 --> 03:17.000
Cassia: She's smaller than

03:15.000 --> 03:17.000
I thought she'd be.

03:17.000 --> 03:27.000
♪♪

03:27.000 --> 03:29.000
♪♪

03:29.000 --> 03:32.000
[ Door closes ]

03:32.000 --> 03:42.000
♪♪

03:42.000 --> 03:45.000
♪♪

03:45.000 --> 03:48.000
[ Static, woman speaking

03:45.000 --> 03:48.000
indistinctly ]

03:49.000 --> 03:51.000
♪♪

03:51.000 --> 03:56.000
♪ The door that finally opens ♪

03:56.000 --> 03:58.000
♪ With light flooding in ♪

03:58.000 --> 04:02.000
♪ Spilling out on the floor ♪

04:02.000 --> 04:04.000
♪♪

04:04.000 --> 04:08.000
♪ The core that never was ♪

04:08.000 --> 04:11.000
♪ Now it will be ♪

04:11.000 --> 04:16.000
♪ The bones of what

04:11.000 --> 04:16.000
was there before ♪

04:17.000 --> 04:19.000
♪ Every step, every beat ♪

04:19.000 --> 04:23.000
♪ Every thought, every breath,

04:19.000 --> 04:23.000
everything ♪

04:23.000 --> 04:30.000
♪ Is longing ♪

04:30.000 --> 04:34.000
♪ Pulling you from the sky ♪

04:34.000 --> 04:37.000
♪ Just like love will do ♪

04:37.000 --> 04:41.000
♪ Pulling you from the ground ♪

04:41.000 --> 04:45.000
♪ Just like love will do ♪

04:45.000 --> 04:52.000
♪♪

05:02.000 --> 05:04.000
[ Door opens, wind whistling ]

05:07.000 --> 05:09.000
I told you

05:07.000 --> 05:09.000
you could do it.

05:09.000 --> 05:12.000
Whoo!

05:18.000 --> 05:20.000
[ Sighs ]

05:20.000 --> 05:22.000
There's my little soldier.

05:22.000 --> 05:25.000
I'm so proud of you.

05:25.000 --> 05:28.000
Are you proud of me,

05:25.000 --> 05:28.000
Mom?

05:28.000 --> 05:30.000
Yeah.

05:30.000 --> 05:33.000
Of course I am.

05:33.000 --> 05:35.000
I'm hungry.

05:33.000 --> 05:35.000
I made a trap.

05:35.000 --> 05:37.000
Makes killing the creatures

05:35.000 --> 05:37.000
really easy.

05:37.000 --> 05:41.000
And what about

05:37.000 --> 05:41.000
the crops?

05:41.000 --> 05:43.000
They're radioactive.

05:43.000 --> 05:45.000
There's some food

05:43.000 --> 05:45.000
in the barracks.

05:45.000 --> 05:47.000
I'll get some

05:45.000 --> 05:47.000
for all of us.

05:47.000 --> 05:49.000
Come right back.

06:10.000 --> 06:11.000
Huh.

06:11.000 --> 06:14.000
[ Beeping ]

06:14.000 --> 06:17.000
♪♪

06:17.000 --> 06:20.000
There's a little life

06:17.000 --> 06:20.000
left in you, huh?

06:20.000 --> 06:22.000
Sue:

06:20.000 --> 06:22.000
You used Paul.

06:22.000 --> 06:24.000
You're no better than

06:22.000 --> 06:24.000
the assholes

06:24.000 --> 06:27.000
that sent you to the front

06:24.000 --> 06:27.000
when you were 12 years old.

06:27.000 --> 06:28.000
I knew

06:27.000 --> 06:28.000
he was gonna be okay.

06:28.000 --> 06:29.000
No, you didn't.

06:29.000 --> 06:31.000
Well,

06:29.000 --> 06:31.000
neither did you.

06:31.000 --> 06:33.000
What should we do?

06:31.000 --> 06:33.000
Call child services?

06:33.000 --> 06:35.000
Have him put in

06:33.000 --> 06:35.000
a more stable home?

06:35.000 --> 06:36.000
Is that

06:35.000 --> 06:36.000
what you want?

06:36.000 --> 06:39.000
No, what I want is to stop

06:36.000 --> 06:39.000
listening to that shit.

06:39.000 --> 06:42.000
We got Paul back.

06:39.000 --> 06:42.000
We don't need them anymore.

06:42.000 --> 06:44.000
You know, back on Earth,

06:42.000 --> 06:44.000
you promised me

06:44.000 --> 06:45.000
that we would

06:44.000 --> 06:45.000
take revenge.

06:45.000 --> 06:46.000
Do you remember?

06:45.000 --> 06:46.000
Go ahead.

06:46.000 --> 06:48.000
Kill 'em all.

06:46.000 --> 06:48.000
I don't need

06:46.000 --> 06:48.000
to kill them.

06:48.000 --> 06:51.000
I just need to ditch them

06:48.000 --> 06:51.000
as soon as possible.

06:51.000 --> 06:53.000
There's one lander here.

06:53.000 --> 06:56.000
I say we take it, we fill it

06:53.000 --> 06:56.000
with as many supplies as we can,

06:56.000 --> 06:58.000
and we head to the tropical

06:56.000 --> 06:58.000
zone, just the three of us.

06:58.000 --> 07:01.000
We just got here.

06:58.000 --> 07:01.000
Give me some time to think.

07:01.000 --> 07:03.000
What's the rush?

07:07.000 --> 07:11.000
Yeah, I know you're having fun

07:07.000 --> 07:11.000
being worshipped,

07:11.000 --> 07:13.000
but that was

07:11.000 --> 07:13.000
a means to an end.

07:13.000 --> 07:16.000
These people

07:13.000 --> 07:16.000
destroyed the Earth.

07:16.000 --> 07:20.000
If we keep this up, we're not

07:16.000 --> 07:20.000
survivors, we're traitors.

07:20.000 --> 07:22.000
Okay, fine.

07:22.000 --> 07:23.000
We can go.

07:23.000 --> 07:27.000
As soon as I reprogram

07:23.000 --> 07:27.000
the two androids, okay?

07:27.000 --> 07:30.000
The service model will be

07:27.000 --> 07:30.000
more than enough to help.

07:30.000 --> 07:32.000
We don't need

07:30.000 --> 07:32.000
the necromancer.

07:32.000 --> 07:33.000
What if

07:32.000 --> 07:33.000
you can't control her?

07:34.000 --> 07:36.000
Be safer

07:34.000 --> 07:36.000
if you destroy her.

07:36.000 --> 07:46.000
♪♪

07:46.000 --> 07:48.000
♪♪

07:48.000 --> 07:49.000
What is it?

07:49.000 --> 07:51.000
Nothing.

07:51.000 --> 07:53.000
♪♪

07:54.000 --> 07:55.000
I'm not

07:54.000 --> 07:55.000
destroying her.

07:55.000 --> 07:57.000
You spent

07:55.000 --> 07:57.000
your whole life

07:57.000 --> 07:59.000
watching those things

07:57.000 --> 07:59.000
slaughter your friends.

07:59.000 --> 08:01.000
I would have thought

07:59.000 --> 08:01.000
you'd want to destroy her.

08:01.000 --> 08:02.000
I know I do.

08:02.000 --> 08:05.000
She's the most powerful weapon

08:02.000 --> 08:05.000
on this planet.

08:05.000 --> 08:07.000
♪♪

08:07.000 --> 08:10.000
What if there's more ships

08:07.000 --> 08:10.000
coming from Earth?

08:10.000 --> 08:11.000
Because without her,

08:11.000 --> 08:14.000
whatever we build

08:11.000 --> 08:14.000
in the tropical zone --

08:14.000 --> 08:16.000
it can be

08:14.000 --> 08:16.000
taken away from us.

08:16.000 --> 08:19.000
♪♪

08:19.000 --> 08:20.000
Fine.

08:21.000 --> 08:22.000
Fine.

08:22.000 --> 08:24.000
♪♪

08:24.000 --> 08:27.000
I'll be with Paul.

08:27.000 --> 08:37.000
♪♪

08:37.000 --> 08:47.000
♪♪

08:47.000 --> 08:57.000
♪♪

08:57.000 --> 09:06.000
♪♪

09:06.000 --> 09:08.000
♪♪

09:08.000 --> 09:09.000
Marcus:

09:08.000 --> 09:09.000
Hello, Lamia.

09:09.000 --> 09:12.000
What have you done

09:09.000 --> 09:12.000
with Campion?

09:15.000 --> 09:17.000
He's in a time-out

09:15.000 --> 09:17.000
at the moment.

09:17.000 --> 09:18.000
And the other children?

09:19.000 --> 09:20.000
They're safe.

09:19.000 --> 09:20.000
Mm.

09:20.000 --> 09:23.000
Now.

09:23.000 --> 09:25.000
You have

09:23.000 --> 09:25.000
your son back.

09:26.000 --> 09:27.000
Let me take my family

09:27.000 --> 09:29.000
and we'll leave here

09:27.000 --> 09:29.000
peacefully.

09:30.000 --> 09:32.000
Your family?

09:32.000 --> 09:34.000
Oh.

09:34.000 --> 09:37.000
You mean the children

09:34.000 --> 09:37.000
that you stole?

09:37.000 --> 09:39.000
They belong with me.

09:39.000 --> 09:41.000
Hmm.

09:41.000 --> 09:43.000
Okay, so,

09:41.000 --> 09:43.000
I should just, um...

09:43.000 --> 09:45.000
take your word

09:43.000 --> 09:45.000
for it?

09:45.000 --> 09:46.000
Just...

09:46.000 --> 09:49.000
let you leave?

09:49.000 --> 09:52.000
I have no reason

09:49.000 --> 09:52.000
to deceive you.

09:52.000 --> 09:53.000
[ Scoffs ] Yeah.

09:54.000 --> 09:57.000
Pretty sure

09:54.000 --> 09:57.000
that you do.

10:01.000 --> 10:03.000
These people

10:01.000 --> 10:03.000
who follow you --

10:03.000 --> 10:06.000
do they know

10:03.000 --> 10:06.000
who you truly are?

10:06.000 --> 10:09.000
♪♪

10:09.000 --> 10:12.000
You changed your face.

10:12.000 --> 10:15.000
Did you change your name

10:12.000 --> 10:15.000
with it?

10:15.000 --> 10:17.000
♪♪

10:17.000 --> 10:20.000
I detected your surgical scars

10:17.000 --> 10:20.000
when we first met.

10:21.000 --> 10:22.000
♪♪

10:22.000 --> 10:25.000
Your original face

10:22.000 --> 10:25.000
was tattooed

10:25.000 --> 10:28.000
when you were

10:25.000 --> 10:28.000
just a child.

10:28.000 --> 10:31.000
You served with

10:28.000 --> 10:31.000
the atheist brigade.

10:31.000 --> 10:34.000
♪♪

10:34.000 --> 10:36.000
Is that why

10:34.000 --> 10:36.000
you didn't kill me?

10:36.000 --> 10:38.000
[ Chuckles ]

10:38.000 --> 10:41.000
We are of a like mind,

10:38.000 --> 10:41.000
you and I.

10:41.000 --> 10:44.000
[ Scoffs, chuckles ]

10:44.000 --> 10:46.000
I don't think so.

10:46.000 --> 10:49.000
Hmm?

10:49.000 --> 10:51.000
See...

10:51.000 --> 10:56.000
♪♪

10:56.000 --> 11:00.000
I've seen

10:56.000 --> 11:00.000
a lot of your kind

11:00.000 --> 11:02.000
kill a lot of mine.

11:02.000 --> 11:06.000
We're not here

11:02.000 --> 11:06.000
to repeat history.

11:06.000 --> 11:07.000
♪♪

11:07.000 --> 11:09.000
And yet,

11:07.000 --> 11:09.000
here we are.

11:09.000 --> 11:12.000
We have an opportunity,

11:09.000 --> 11:12.000
you and I,

11:12.000 --> 11:16.000
to shape

11:12.000 --> 11:16.000
the future of humanity,

11:16.000 --> 11:17.000
to build a civilization

11:17.000 --> 11:21.000
founded on humanity's belief

11:17.000 --> 11:21.000
in itself.

11:21.000 --> 11:23.000
♪♪

11:23.000 --> 11:25.000
Think about it.

11:25.000 --> 11:28.000
No war.

11:28.000 --> 11:30.000
No suffering.

11:28.000 --> 11:30.000
[ Chuckles ]

11:30.000 --> 11:34.000
Whoever reprogrammed you

11:30.000 --> 11:34.000
did a hell of a job.

11:34.000 --> 11:37.000
For a second there, I actually

11:34.000 --> 11:37.000
thought that you cared.

11:37.000 --> 11:38.000
Hmm.

11:37.000 --> 11:38.000
[ Chuckles ]

11:39.000 --> 11:41.000
Preserving humanity

11:39.000 --> 11:41.000
has always been my mission.

11:41.000 --> 11:45.000
Well, it hasn't been

11:41.000 --> 11:45.000
very successful, then, has it?

11:45.000 --> 11:48.000
Considering you killed

11:45.000 --> 11:48.000
all those people on the ark,

11:48.000 --> 11:51.000
including

11:48.000 --> 11:51.000
all of those children

11:51.000 --> 11:52.000
that you did not

11:51.000 --> 11:52.000
take with you.

11:53.000 --> 11:55.000
Then why haven't you

11:53.000 --> 11:55.000
destroyed me?

11:55.000 --> 12:04.000
♪♪

12:04.000 --> 12:06.000
What were you doing

12:04.000 --> 12:06.000
in the sim?

12:07.000 --> 12:09.000
Why did you keep

12:07.000 --> 12:09.000
going back there?

12:09.000 --> 12:11.000
Hmm?

12:11.000 --> 12:13.000
Must have been

12:11.000 --> 12:13.000
pretty special

12:13.000 --> 12:17.000
for you to let your guard down

12:13.000 --> 12:17.000
like that.

12:17.000 --> 12:18.000
What's wrong?

12:18.000 --> 12:20.000
Hmm?

12:20.000 --> 12:23.000
Reality not

12:20.000 --> 12:23.000
good enough for you?

12:23.000 --> 12:33.000
♪♪

12:33.000 --> 12:35.000
Hmm.

12:35.000 --> 12:45.000
♪♪

12:45.000 --> 12:49.000
♪♪

12:49.000 --> 12:51.000
[ Sighs ]

12:51.000 --> 12:53.000
No one goes in there

12:51.000 --> 12:53.000
but me.

12:53.000 --> 12:55.000
Yes,

12:53.000 --> 12:55.000
Your Eminence.

12:55.000 --> 13:02.000
♪♪

13:02.000 --> 13:07.000
Together: I walk the path of

13:02.000 --> 13:07.000
the sun and gaze upon his glory.

13:07.000 --> 13:10.000
Let the light break forth

13:07.000 --> 13:10.000
to thee,

13:10.000 --> 13:16.000
our only conservation now,

13:10.000 --> 13:16.000
our future of great reward.

13:16.000 --> 13:20.000
Oh, Sol thyself,

13:16.000 --> 13:20.000
please be our guide,

13:20.000 --> 13:22.000
and draw our souls to thee.

13:22.000 --> 13:27.000
Shade of night and morning ray,

13:22.000 --> 13:27.000
took from thee the name of day.

13:27.000 --> 13:30.000
Listen to our mournful cry.

13:30.000 --> 13:33.000
Now again, the shades are nigh.

13:33.000 --> 13:36.000
♪♪

13:36.000 --> 13:38.000
Vita: Father.

13:38.000 --> 13:40.000
They fixed you.

13:40.000 --> 13:42.000
Remove yourself

13:40.000 --> 13:42.000
from my hand, child.

13:42.000 --> 13:44.000
You will hinder

13:42.000 --> 13:44.000
my performance.

13:45.000 --> 13:54.000
♪♪

13:55.000 --> 14:00.000
♪♪

14:00.000 --> 14:02.000
He's not Father anymore.

14:02.000 --> 14:04.000
Then...

14:02.000 --> 14:04.000
who is he?

14:04.000 --> 14:07.000
He's just an android now,

14:04.000 --> 14:07.000
Vita.

14:11.000 --> 14:14.000
Lucius: Hunter told me your

14:11.000 --> 14:14.000
pendants been taken from you.

14:14.000 --> 14:17.000
These belonged

14:14.000 --> 14:17.000
to the soldiers

14:17.000 --> 14:19.000
that died

14:17.000 --> 14:19.000
in the attack.

14:24.000 --> 14:28.000
They would have wanted you

14:24.000 --> 14:28.000
to have them.

14:31.000 --> 14:33.000
Nice.

14:31.000 --> 14:33.000
Praise Sol.

14:33.000 --> 14:34.000
Praise Sol.

14:34.000 --> 14:35.000
Praise Sol.

14:36.000 --> 14:38.000
What's gonna happen

14:36.000 --> 14:38.000
to Campion?

14:38.000 --> 14:40.000
He needs

14:38.000 --> 14:40.000
to be baptized.

14:40.000 --> 14:44.000
He's impure

14:40.000 --> 14:44.000
and not fit to speak to.

14:44.000 --> 14:46.000
Do you understand?

14:57.000 --> 15:00.000
What are you doing?

15:00.000 --> 15:01.000
You're gonna

15:00.000 --> 15:01.000
curse yourself.

15:01.000 --> 15:03.000
We're already cursed.

15:03.000 --> 15:04.000
Don't, Vita.

15:04.000 --> 15:06.000
We need

15:04.000 --> 15:06.000
to sneak Campion some food.

15:06.000 --> 15:07.000
You heard the soldier.

15:07.000 --> 15:09.000
We shouldn't go near him

15:07.000 --> 15:09.000
until he's been baptized.

15:09.000 --> 15:11.000
You knew

15:09.000 --> 15:11.000
they were coming.

15:11.000 --> 15:13.000
You could have warned

15:11.000 --> 15:13.000
Mother and Father.

15:13.000 --> 15:15.000
I expect it from Hunter,

15:13.000 --> 15:15.000
but you --

15:15.000 --> 15:17.000
The androids

15:15.000 --> 15:17.000
killed our people.

15:17.000 --> 15:18.000
They kidnapped us,

15:17.000 --> 15:18.000
Tempest.

